Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(960,1014)\fad(150,150)\b0\bord3.375\shad2.7\fnDumpling-Regular\fs74.25}‫זום, זום, זום, זום
